---
import Layout from '/src/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Melbourne Disc Golf Club" subtitle="Building community through disc golf since 2008">
	
	<main>

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="prose lg:prose-lg mx-auto">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
					<p>
						Founded in 2008, the Melbourne Disc Golf Club is a not-for-profit organisation 
						managed by a voluntary committee. We have a simple goal - to create a local 
						community of players and to spread awareness of this enjoyable, challenging 
						and environmentally responsible sport.
					</p>

					<h2>Our Community</h2>
					<p>
						Membership is open to all ages and abilities. Our current membership ranges 
						from 9 to 70+ years old, so whether you're young or old, super competitive 
						or just want to have fun, there's a place for you in our club.
					</p>

					<h2>How We Play</h2>
					<p>
						Some members play socially in monthly events, while others compete in 
						tournaments including:
					</p>
					<ul>
						<li>State championships</li>
						<li>National Championships</li>
						<li>US Disc Golf Championships</li>
						<li>World Championships</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>Mission & Values</h2>
					<p>
						We believe disc golf is an enjoyable, challenging and environmentally 
						responsible sport that brings people together. Our focus is on building 
						an inclusive community where players of all skill levels can enjoy the game.
					</p>

					<div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
						<h3 class="text-green-800 font-semibold mb-4">Ready to Join?</h3>
						<p class="text-green-700 mb-4">
							Whether you're new to disc golf or an experienced player, we'd love to welcome you to our community.
						</p>
						<div class="space-x-4">
							<a href="/club/membership" class="bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
								Learn About Membership
							</a>
							<a href="/disc-golf" class="bg-white text-green-600 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg border border-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 transition-colors">
								What is Disc Golf?
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>